<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>صوابه عمران وعنه ابنه محمد* <span class="c2">(٢)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠٤)</span> <span class="c2">(عمرو)</span> برق هر ابن عبد الله تقدم<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
